    "description": "We at Marathon Realty Asia Pacific Associates are looking for an experienced Senior Property Advisor based out of Kanpur. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Marathon Realty Asia Pacific Associates:\nMarathon Realty Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in Lease Administration\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Learning & development budget\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kanpur, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Marathon Realty Asia Pacific Associates!",
